title: Import player by eBIS ID
custom_preconds: GIVEN user is logged in as Fed Admin
custom_steps: WHEN entering an eBIS ID and Clicking "Create Player"
custom_expected:
THEN the match modal will be displayed
AND clicking "Import Profile" will import the players profile

title: Import player by name
custom_preconds: GIVEN user is logged in as Fed Admin
custom_steps: WHEN entering first/last/birth country/birth date and Clicking "Create Player"
custom_expected:
THEN the match modal will be displayed
AND clicking "Import Profile" will import the players profile

title: Adding a document from the interest list
custom_preconds: GIVEN user is viewing the Interest List
custom_steps:
WHEN launching the options menu and clicking "player docs"
AND adding a document and saving
custom_expected: THEN "submit for eligibility" will become active on the options menu

title: Submit for eligibility and approve
custom_preconds: GIVEN "submit for eligibility" is enabled for a player
custom_steps:
WHEN submitting a player for eligibility
AND navigating to the Player Eligibility clipboard
AND clicking "Approve"
custom_expected:
THEN on the Interest List "Approved" will be displayed in the Eligibility column
AND the player will be added to the Available list

title: Submit for eligibility and deny
custom_preconds: GIVEN "submit for eligibility" is enabled for a player
custom_steps:
WHEN submitting a player for eligibility
AND navigating to the Player Eligibility clipboard
AND clicking "Deny"
AND entering denial comments
AND clicking "Deny"
custom_expected:
THEN "Denied" will be displayed on the Eligibility column
AND "submit for eligibility" will become enabled again

title: Transfer to Provisional Roster
custom_preconds: GIVEN a player has been added to the available list
custom_expected: THEN the player will appear in the players section of the Provisional Roster

title: Transfer to Final Roster
custom_preconds:
GIVEn a Player has been added to the Provisional Roster
AND a document with a PPA label has been added
custom_steps:
WHEN dragging and dropping a player to the final roster
AND clicking save
custom_expected:
THEN the player will be added to the final roster
AND the drag and drop feature will be disabled

title: Matching to a player already on your prospective players list by eBIS ID
custom_preconds: GIVEN a player on the prospective players list isn't on the interest list
custom_expected:
THEN the match modal will be displayed
AND the add to interest button will be displayed in the system matches column

title: Matching to a player already on your prospective players list by name
custom_preconds: GIVEN a player on the prospective players list isn't on the interest list
custom_steps: WHEN entering their first/last/birth country/ dob
custom_expected:
THEN the match modal will be displayed
AND the add to interest button will be displayed in the system matches column

title: Matching to a player already on your interest list by eBIS ID
custom_preconds: GIVEN a player has been added to the interest list
custom_steps:
WHEN entering their eBIS ID 
AND clicking create player
custom_expected:
THEN the match modal will be displayed
AND the add to interest list button will be disabled

title: Matching to a player already on your interest list by name
